      <h2>Best International Credit Cards in India</h2>
      <p>International credit cards are specifically designed for people who travel frequently, shop from global websites, pay for international subscriptions, or make business payments abroad. These cards run on globally accepted networks like Visa and Mastercard, ensuring seamless acceptance at millions of merchants across 200+ countries and online platforms worldwide.</p>
      <p>Beyond acceptance, the best international cards offer competitive forex markup rates (0-2% vs. 3.5% on regular cards), comprehensive global travel insurance, emergency card replacement anywhere in the world, and 24/7 international customer support. For NRIs, students studying abroad, and business travellers, an international credit card is an essential financial tool.</p>

      <h2>Key Features of International Credit Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Worldwide Acceptance:</strong> Visa and Mastercard networks ensure acceptance at 80 million+ merchants across 200+ countries</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Low Forex Markup:</strong> International cards charge 0-2% markup compared to 3.5% on standard cards, saving significantly on foreign spends</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Global Travel Insurance:</strong> Covers air accidents, medical emergencies, lost baggage, trip cancellation, and passport loss</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Emergency Replacement:</strong> Get a replacement card delivered anywhere in the world within 48-72 hours if lost or stolen</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>24/7 International Support:</strong> Dedicated helpline accessible from any country for card issues and travel assistance</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Multi-Currency Settlement:</strong> Transact seamlessly in 150+ currencies with real-time conversion at competitive rates</li>
      </ul>

